    "AI research in Indonesia in linguistics has been carried out, including the work by Yudono (2023) examining AI's ability to write short horror stories.",
    "Research (Prastiwi & Pujiawati, 2019) examines the combination of Artificial Intelligence (Paperrater) with natural intelligence in learning to write English."
  ]
